'''Hydroponics stations''',<ref name="HD" /> also known as '''agridomes''',<ref name="GG1-2">[[Galaxy Guide 1: A New Hope (Second Edition)|''Galaxy Guide 1: A New Hope'', Second Edition]]</ref> were used to grow [[Fruit/Legends|fruits]] and [[Vegetable/Legends|vegetables]].<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Premiere Limited|cardname=Hydroponics Station}}</ref> Common on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]],<ref name="HD" /> they were often located underground and made efficient use of [[Water/Legends|water]] to irrigate the crops. Hydroponics stations were often used by [[Moisture farmer/Legends|moisture farmers]] to feed their families, with any excess produce being sold at markets.<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Premiere Limited|cardname=Hydroponics Station}}</ref> Moisture farmers who sold produce did so as a side business, generating [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] to buy supplies and the occasional luxury. Some moisture [[Farmer/Legends|farmers]] found that growing food was a more profitable business than water production.<ref name="GG1-2" />

